      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW TRINNY (1) turned in a plain run last time when seventh at Warragul over 400m behind Paw Qatar (23.61) in a Grade 5. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Key runner on her best form. TINKER DREW (2) filled a minor placing last start at Ballarat behind Cheetah Moon (22.54) in a Grade 5. Led around the bend before fighting on well and should give a sight. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings five times from six starts. Expected to be in the finish again. PAW PASCAL (7) has a solid strike rate at this track and distance.",
